<div class="mail" style="font-family:Arial">
  <header style="padding: 1.5em; background-color: #4888FF; box-shadow: 1px 1px 4px #303030;">
    <h1 class="email-title"><a href="http://hobby-swap.co" style="color: white;letter-spacing: 0.05em;text-decoration: none;">HobbySwap</a></h1>
    <h2 style="font-size: 0.8em;color: white;">COMPLETED TRADE SUMMARY</h2>
  </header>
  <article style="text-align: center;color: #303030;margin: 0 10%;">
    <div class="email-details">
      <div class="transaction-summary">
        <h2 class="summary-title">SUMMARY OF TRANSACTION #{{ tid }}</h2>
        <h2 class="users" style="font-weight: 400;">Trade made between: <a href="https://hobby-swap.co/user/{{ responder.id }}">{{ responder.name }}</a> and <a href="https://hobby-swap.co/user/{{ requester.id }}">{{ requester.name }}</a></h2>
        <div class="items-container" style="display: flex;width: 80%;margin: 40px 10%;column-gap: 50px;">
          <div class="responder-items" style="flex-basis: 50%;display: flex;flex-direction: column;">
            <h2 class="items-label" style="width: 80%;margin: 0 10%;padding: 10px 0;border-radius: 10px 10px 0 0;background-color: #4888FF;color: white;">{{ responder.name }} traded:</h2>
            {% for item in responder.items %}
              <div class="item" style="background-color: #F3F3F3;border-radius: 5px;border-left: 8px solid #4888FF;margin-bottom: 15px;">
                <h3 class="item-title" style="margin: 0;"><a href="http://hobby-swap.co/node/1" style="display: block;text-decoration: none;color: #303030;font-size: 1.5rem;font-weight: 400;margin: 0 10%;border-bottom: 2px solid #B5B5B5;padding: 10px 0;">{{ item.title }}</a></h3>
                <h3 class="item-value" style="color: #FFDD47;font-size: 1.5rem;text-shadow: 1px 1px #B5B5B5;display: flex;align-items: center;column-gap: 5px;justify-content: center;margin: 0 10%;padding: 10px 0;">{{ item.value }}<span style="text-shadow: none;display: block;border: 3px solid #FFDD47;font-size: 0.5em;line-height: 0.5em;padding: 0.4em 0.2em;clip-path: polygon(0% 50%, 50% 0%, 100% 0%, 100% 50%, 50% 100%, 0% 100%);">H</span></h3>
              </div>
            {% endfor %}
            {% if residual > 0 %}
              <div class="item residual" style="background-color: #F3F3F3;border-radius: 5px;border-left: 8px solid #4888FF;margin-bottom: 15px;border-color: #ffdd47;">
                <h3 class="item-value" style="color: #FFDD47;font-size: 1.5rem;text-shadow: 1px 1px #B5B5B5;display: flex;align-items: center;column-gap: 5px;justify-content: center;margin: 0 10%;padding: 10px 0;">+ {{ residual }}<span style="text-shadow: none;display: block;border: 3px solid #FFDD47;font-size: 0.5em;line-height: 0.5em;padding: 0.4em 0.2em;clip-path: polygon(0% 50%, 50% 0%, 100% 0%, 100% 50%, 50% 100%, 0% 100%);">H</span></h3>
              </div>
            {% endif %}
          </div>
          <div class="requester-items" style="flex-basis: 50%;display: flex;flex-direction: column;">
            <h2 class="items-label" style="width: 80%;margin: 0 10%;padding: 10px 0;border-radius: 10px 10px 0 0;background-color: #4888FF;color: white;">{{ requester.name }} traded:</h2>
            {% for item in requester.items %}
              <div class="item" style="background-color: #F3F3F3;border-radius: 5px;border-left: 8px solid #4888FF;margin-bottom: 15px;">
                <h3 class="item-title" style="margin: 0;"><a href="http://hobby-swap.co/node/1" style="display: block;text-decoration: none;color: #303030;font-size: 1.5rem;font-weight: 400;margin: 0 10%;border-bottom: 2px solid #B5B5B5;padding: 10px 0;">{{ item.title }}</a></h3>
                <h3 class="item-value" style="color: #FFDD47;font-size: 1.5rem;text-shadow: 1px 1px #B5B5B5;display: flex;align-items: center;column-gap: 5px;justify-content: center;margin: 0 10%;padding: 10px 0;">{{ item.value }}<span style="text-shadow: none;display: block;border: 3px solid #FFDD47;font-size: 0.5em;line-height: 0.5em;padding: 0.4em 0.2em;clip-path: polygon(0% 50%, 50% 0%, 100% 0%, 100% 50%, 50% 100%, 0% 100%);">H</span></h3>
              </div>
            {% endfor %}
            {% if residual < 0 %}
              <div class="item residual" style="background-color: #F3F3F3;border-radius: 5px;border-left: 8px solid #4888FF;margin-bottom: 15px;border-color: #ffdd47;">
                <h3 class="item-value" style="color: #FFDD47;font-size: 1.5rem;text-shadow: 1px 1px #B5B5B5;display: flex;align-items: center;column-gap: 5px;justify-content: center;margin: 0 10%;padding: 10px 0;">+ {{ residual|abs }}<span style="text-shadow: none;display: block;border: 3px solid #FFDD47;font-size: 0.5em;line-height: 0.5em;padding: 0.4em 0.2em;clip-path: polygon(0% 50%, 50% 0%, 100% 0%, 100% 50%, 50% 100%, 0% 100%);">H</span></h3>
              </div>
            {% endif %}
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="user-emails">
          <h2 style="margin: 50px 20% 0 20%;">In the case that the users involved would like to privately contact each other, the email for each user has been listed below to facilitate further contact.</h2>
          <h3 style="display: inline-block;border: 4px solid #F3F3F3;border-radius: 3px;padding: 5px;font-weight: 400;"><span style="color: #4888FF;">{{ responder.name }}:</span> {{ responder.email }}</h3>
          <h3 style="display: inline-block;border: 4px solid #F3F3F3;border-radius: 3px;padding: 5px;font-weight: 400;"><span style="color: #4888FF;">{{ requester.name }}:</span> {{ requester.email }}</h3>
        </div>
        <div class="exchange-policy" style="margin: 50px 10%;">
          <h2>Shipping at HobbySwap is currently dependent on users acting in good faith</h2>
          <p>While it is our intent to include shipping integration in the future, today we do not have the resources to
            coordinate preprocessed shipment of traded items. If users intend to exchange their items via a parcel service,
            it must be coordinated by those individuals. HobbySwap cannot be held responsible for any type of malicious
            exchange such as: intentional failure to mail items, mailing incorrect items, or misleading listings. In its
            current form, HobbySwap aims to efficiently manage a transaction between two users so that they can settle upon
            a favorable agreement. Although HobbySwap has put systems in place to ensure the validity of its users, it still
            remains the responsibility of the user to cautiously evaluate each exchange. Trade Safe.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="discord-container" style="margin: 2em 25% 1em 25%;padding: 1em;border-radius: 0.2em;background-color: #4888FF;position: relative;">
        <h3 class="discord-info" style="margin: auto;height: fit-content;text-align: center;border-right: 4px solid #FFDD47;border-left: 4px solid #FFDD47;font-weight: 500;padding: 0 0.5em;color: white;">If you haven't already, join our Discord server to see announcements, find out more about HobbySwap, and to be a part of the community</h3>
        <a class="discord-link" href="http://hobby-swap.co/discord" style="display: block;flex: 1;width: fit-content;padding: 0.5em;margin: 0.5em auto 0 auto;text-decoration: none;color: #303030;background-color: white;border-radius: 0.2em;font-size: 2em;font-weight: 800;">JOIN</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </article>
  <footer style="padding: 1.5em;background-color: #4888FF;text-align: center;">
    <h2 class="email-footer">For more information about HobbySwap, go to <a href="http://hobby-swap.co/about" style="color: white;transition: color 0.2s;">hobby-swap.co/about</a></h2>
  </footer>
</div>
